author: marrs
msg: Refactored the client UI code. Instead of a mix of HTML layout and code based layout, every control is now generated and placed from code. A logo at the top is the only exception. Styling is done in the CSS, and more styling has been added.

author: markt
msg: Expose filters via JMX. Filter config is now available via JMX in read-only form.
Based on a patch provided by Xie Xiaodong as part of GSOC2009.
